T02TD1739E:106b-4: / rje btsun ma sgrol ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1739E:106b-5: bsnyen pa yongs rdzogs rnal 'byor pas //
T02TD1739E:106b-6: bar chod bzlog pa'i cho ga brtsams //
T02TD1739E:106b-7: dben pa'i gnas su mandala dang //
T02TD1739E:106b-8: mchod pa gtor ma bshams la ni //
T02TD1739E:106b-9: bskyed pa'i rim pa rdzogs bsgoms la //
T02TD1739E:106b-10: mchod pa bstod pa dus gsum dbul //
T02TD1739E:106b-11: de nas snying gar rtsa bsams la //
T02TD1739E:106b-12: zhu bas 'khor lo rtsibs bzhir gyur //
T02TD1739E:106b-13: lte ba stong pa'i nang nyid du //
T02TD1739E:106b-14: bdag nyid lha yi rnal 'byor gnas //
T02TD1739E:106b-15: rtsibs gnyis rtse la gri gug bsam //
T02TD1739E:106b-16: gnyis pa ral gri me 'bar bsam //
T02TD1739E:106b-18: 'khor lo de la mtshon cha ni //
T02TD1739E:106b-19: char pa bab pas gsod par bsam //
T02TD1739E:106b-21: aom hr'im trim dha ra dhad /
T02TD1739E:106b-22: tsa kra lo ka m'a ra ya m'a ra ya /
T02TD1739E:106b-27: de ltar drag po'i sngags bzlas pas ;
T02TD1739E:106b-30: gzhan gyi rig sngags smod pa dang //
T02TD1739E:106b-31: gdon dang bar chod gang yin pa //
T02TD1739E:106b-32: bkug la 'khor lo mtshon chas gtub //
T02TD1739E:106b-33: ting 'dzin gsal dang bzlas pa ni //
T02TD1739E:106b-34: brtson pas rab tu 'bad par bya ;
T02TD1739E:106b-35: / de ltar zhag ni lnga'am bdun //
T02TD1739E:106b-36: gsum gsum bar du byas gyur na //
T02TD1739E:106b-37: phyag na rdo rje'i stobs kyang rdugs //
T02TD1739E:106b-38: phyir bzlog 'khor lo slob dpon rtag pa'i rdo rjes mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD1739E:106b-40: // / mkhas pa chen po rma ban chos 'bar gyis bsgyur ba'o//
